180
00:09:42,000 --> 00:09:48,000
[SPEAKER_03] Program traje 14 tjedana, a prijavi se vrše putem online obrazca ili putem e-maila.

181
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:54,000
[SPEAKER_03] Evo, Bruno, jel' se čujemo?

182
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:58,000
